Participants face:

* Time-consuming supplier requalification
* Loss of visibility into cross-organizational intelligence
* Rebuilding risk forecasting from scratch
* Lack of historical audit evidence for regulatory compliance
* Weakening of long-term procurement strategy

This creates **behavioral and strategic lock-in**, even if alternatives exist.

